title: Space - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/27/22
itunes:title: Space - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/27/22
description:
George Noory and astronomer Steven Kates discuss the latest developments in space exploration, including Russia's decision to no longer participate in the international space station, plans for future moon landings, and dangerous solar flares that could destroy Earth's power grid.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
